  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4417580/extras/61802f2ef5d499814229f76bf94f7f96.avif?t=1773911445\" width=720 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Soul Requiem\" is a 2D action roguelite featuring a unique emotion-based combat system. Wield a spear to strike down corrupted kin and fallen gods, using \"Memory\" shards gathered in battle to empower your character. Experience an intense journey to rescue your mother’s soul through ever-changing emotional synergies and punishing boss encounters.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4417580/extras/61802f2ef5d499814229f76bf94f7f96.avif?t=1773911445\" width=720 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Soul Requiem\" is a 2D action roguelite featuring a unique emotion-based combat system. Wield a spear to strike down corrupted kin and fallen gods, using \"Memory\" shards gathered in battle to empower your character. Experience an intense journey to rescue your mother’s soul through ever-changing emotional synergies and punishing boss encounters.</p>",
